✨ Features

Authority Admin is a complete, modern administration panel for Minecraft servers built entirely around a clean GUI experience. Forget memorizing commands — every action lives behind a single /admin menu packed with live server stats, one-click tools, and full player management capabilities.

What it does
Managing your server should feel fast and intuitive. Authority Admin gives your staff team a fully visual control panel where they can punish, monitor, and manage players without ever leaving the game. From banning and muting to viewing someone's inventory or applying potion effects — it all happens through polished, responsive GUIs.

Core Features
Punishment System — Permanent and temporary bans, IP bans, mutes, kicks, and warnings with full history tracking. Auto-actions trigger automatically when players reach warning thresholds.

Player Reports — Players can report others in-game. Staff receive instant notifications and manage all reports through a dedicated panel with status tracking (Open, Closed, Dismissed).

Bug Reports — Players submit categorized bug reports (Crash, Gameplay, Performance, Exploit, Other) directly in-game. Staff investigate and track each report through a full workflow: Open → In Progress → Resolved.

Admin Mode Hotbar — Toggle a specialized 9-tool hotbar with quick access to player lists, vanish, freeze, reports, economy, staff chat, and server management. Everything at your fingertips without opening a single menu.

Vanish — Disappear completely with fake leave/join messages. Staff with the right permission can still see you.

Freeze — Lock a player in place during investigations. Block movement and optionally block commands while frozen.

Server Management — Set time, change weather, kill mobs, clear item drops, teleport all players, broadcast messages, and run console commands — all from one GUI.

Economy Integration — Manage player balances, deposit, set, and reset money through the GUI. Powered by Vault.

PlaceholderAPI Support — Expose player punishment and status data to scoreboards, tab lists, and other plugins.

Discord Webhooks — Log every punishment, player report, and bug report to Discord with rich embeds. Supports a dedicated channel for bug reports separately from the main moderation log.

10 Languages — English, Spanish, Portuguese (BR), German, French, Chinese (Simplified), Russian, Japanese, Korean, and Italian. Auto-locale detection supported.

SQLite & MySQL — Works out of the box with SQLite. Switch to MySQL with a single config change for multi-server setups.

Requirements
Paper 1.21.4+
Java 21+
Vault (optional — for economy features)
PlaceholderAPI (optional — for placeholder support)
